data.description: This exceptionally maintained 2019 Dimora built home comes with 2 lots (appx. .51 acre). True pride of ownership inside and out! Upgraded wood-style tile flooring flows throughout. Open concept living/dining/kitchen area is perfect for entertaining with an abundance of windows overlooking the private back yard. The primary bedroom (MIL plan) is large with luxurious bath that offers soaking tub, dual vanity, huge walk-in shower & walk-in closet. The two front rooms have gorgeous plantation shutters. Enjoy the outdoors from your enormous covered patio in back with wonderful view. Popular Tahitian Village with features Colorado River access for fishing, kayaking & swimming with wonderful Pine Forest Golf Course & Lost Pines Nature Trails. Convenient to dining/shopping in Bastrop + a short drive to Austin, Tesla & Airport.
